Package: cbbreadr
Title: Quickly Access College Basketball Data
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: person("John", "Edwards", , "edwards1860@gmail.com", role =
        c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0002-8533-7504"))
Description: Quickly pull in cached data from
        <https://collegebasketballdata.com>. Load in play-by-play,
        game, roster, and other miscellaneous college basketball data
        objects into R as dataframes. Designed for use in performing
        college basketball analytics and modeling work.
